'''''Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds: Clone Campaigns''''' is an [[Wikipedia:Computer game expansion pack|expansion pack]] to the ''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds]]'' video game that was released shortly after the theatrical release of [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']]. It introduced two more playable civilizations and two more campaigns: that of the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]] and the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. Actually an "interquel," it also added new features and updates to the game corpus that affected all the campaigns.

The ''Clone Campaigns'' expansion added more units, such as the [[Decimator (war machine)|Decimator]] and the [[Air cruiser]], [[Power droid/Legends|support for movable power supplies]], and more.

==Plot summary==
===Missions===
[[File:First_Battle_of_Tatooine.jpg|thumb|Sev'rance Tann meets with [[Boorka]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] prior to the [[First Battle of Tatooine]].]]
*In the '''[[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]]''' campaign, your hero is [[Sev'rance Tann/Legends|Sev'rance Tann]], and [[Count/Legends|Count]] [[Dooku/Legends|Dooku]] guides you. Your goal is to capture the energy-mining platforms of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] so that you can effectively hold [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] hostage.
**[[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|Battle of Geonosis]]
**[[Battle of Kaer Orbital Platform]]
**[[First Battle of Tatooine]]
**[[Battle of Eredenn]]
**[[Battle of Alaris Prime (Hunt for the Decimator)|Battle of Alaris Prime]]
**[[Battle of Asteroid 426]]
**[[Assault on Sarapin|First Battle of Sarapin]]

*In the '''Galactic Republic''' campaign, [[Mace Windu/Legends|Mace Windu]] tells you what to do as you control [[Echuu Shen-Jon]], a [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] you meet "later" in the Rebel campaign. Your goal is to get back the energy platforms.
**Battle of Geonosis
**[[Recapture of Sarapin|Second Battle of Sarapin]]
**[[Second Battle of Tatooine]]
**[[Battle of Aereen]]
**[[Battle of Krant]]
**[[Liberation of Coruscant (Galactic Civil War)|The Taking of Coruscant (BONUS MISSION)]] (actually [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]])

