===Cheats===
While playing, press Enter to open up the chat screen. Type one of the following codes and press Enter again. Some codes only work when you highlight a unit.
*'''suddenly silenced''' - Buildings/turrets and units do extra damage.
*'''forcefood''' - Grants the player 1000 Food.
*'''forcecarbon''' - Grants the player 1000 Carbon.
*'''forcenova''' - Grants the player 1000 Nova.
*'''forceore''' - Grants the player 1000 Ore.
*'''Simonsays''' - Grants the player a killer Ewok.
*'''intensify the forward fire power''' - Ground units become stronger.
*'''the fighters are coming in too fast''' - Aircraft become faster.
*'''the most powerful jedi''' - Jedi/Sith become stronger.
*'''the force is strong with this one''' - Jedi/Sith converting becomes faster.
*'''that's no moon''' - Get a [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]].
*'''imperial entanglements''' - Get a [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]].
*'''tantive IV''' - Get a [[CR90 corvette/Legends|Rebel Blockade Runner]].
*'''galactic upheaval''' - Get a Decimator.
*'''skywalker''' - win current mission
*'''tarkin''' - destroy all enemies
*'''scaryneighbor''' - powerful speed boat
*'''forcesight''' - remove/replace fog
*'''forceexplore''' - reveal map

==Continuity==
Similar to the original game, ''Clone Campaigns'' features several [[Easter egg (virtual)|easter eggs]] that can only be found in hard-to-reach areas. These are often non-canon cameos of ''Star Wars'' characters.
*[[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]] are near a [[Sith Temple (Krant)|Sith Temple]] in one mission based on [[Krant]].
*[[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]], Senator [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé Amidala]], [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] can be found on another Krant mission.
*[[Jar Jar Binks/Legends|Jar Jar Binks]] and [[Bossk/Legends|Bossk]] can be seen among the skyscrapers of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].
*C-3PO, R2-D2, [[IG-88D/Legends|IG-88]] and several droids, [[Jawa/Legends|Jawas]] and a [[Sandcrawler/Legends|Sandcrawler]] make a cameo on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].

